long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Skybound Reverie transforms your browser into a breathtaking vista of vibrant skies, where the serene hues of sunset blend seamlessly with the tranquility of floating clouds. The hot air balloon adds a sense of wanderlust, perfect for those who dream of adventure.
Features:

- Stunning Background
- Customizable Shortcuts
- Integrated Clock and Weather
- News
